title: Wild-Card Weekend Reaction Part 2
description:
Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti provide their immediate reactions and analysis to the Cleveland Browns finally ending their playoff wins drought (0:35), the Ravens enacting revenge against the Titans (18:45), and the Nickelodeon madness of the Bears and Saints game (31:45).
